

#### Install SqlDeveloper ####

    1  - Download swldeveloper package  ->  http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/developer-tools/sql-developer/downloads/index.html
    2  - Navigate to download directory  ->  sudo alien --scripts -d sqldeveloper-4.0.0.13.80-1.noarch.rpm
    3  - sudo dpkg --install sqldeveloper_4.0.0.13.80-2_all.deb
    4  - sudo mkdir <path/.sqldeveloper>
    5  - sudo /opt/sqldeveloper/sqldeveloper.sh 
    6  - /usr/lib/jvm/java-7-oracle